HEADWORD: Sneezeweed
<hw>Sneeze"weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A yellow-flowered composite plant (<spn>Helenium autumnale</spn>)
the odor of which is said to cause sneezing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

